CustomField.description: Specifies how target link is opened in the browser. Valid values include "_self" to open in the same tab, and "_blank" to open in a new window or tab.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Specifies how target link is opened in the browser. Valid values include "_self" to open in the same tab, and "_blank" to open in a new window or tab.
CustomField.label: Link Target
